{"tid":1341764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"過埋今晚根本唔撚洗再理民意！","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:33.000Z","uid":26087,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cefec9d1411bb09c79bb412767281134cbdc4977","tid":1341764,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母火都嚟，自己有眼睇到今晚到底發生緊啲咩事。<br />\n<br />\n成班比黑社會打到流嗮血入院，議員黑社會警察互相勾結，中環班黑警今晚咁都要開槍。<br />\n<br />\n如果身邊嘅人仲係未撚醒仲覺得政府同黑警岩嘅根本唔洗理，因為呢班人已經完全失去左做人應有嘅同理心同埋獨立思考能力。<br />\n<br />\n民意已經歸撚嗮邊，兄弟爬山唔督灰唔割席。<br />\n<br />\n我姑且比你班一毛話黑警仲有好人，但過撚埋今晚仲做緊黑警未辭職嘅，下次見到可以唔撚洗講多口水，呢班人係無人性嘅人類渣滓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3706c3871c36adcf1591cb5b0a5f5b800ceb0f0e","tid":1341764,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9370e4862b578f6db3db9b75834ec53016e3389e","tid":1341764,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}